msgctxt "talk01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>But Link...<2.pa> There is something I wish\n"
"to ask you.\n"
"\n"
"<3.so>You journeyed within <4.se_co>Ruta<5.re_co>, the Divine\n"
"Beast of Water...\n"
"\n"
"<6.so>Now you are back, but Mipha has still\n"
"yet to return...\n"
"\n"
"<7.so>Is it as I feared?<8.pa> Were we too late?<9.si_ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (20f)
msgctxt "talk02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Her spirit?!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"So that means Mipha really is...<2.pa>\n"
"Did...did she say anything to you?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (20f)
#. 3: sound
