msgctxt "talk04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I see. My dear Mipha...<2.pa> I simply cannot\n"
"believe it. There was nothing I could do\n"
"to save her...\n"
"<3.so>Still...<4.pa> Mipha fulfilled her heroic duty\n"
"as Champion.\n"
"\n"
"And she will never be alone...<5.pa>\n"
"It is my duty as her father to\n"
"watch over her, even now.\n"
"...<6.pa>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<7.so>Link...<8.pa>\n"
"She really loved you, you know.\n"
"\n"
"<9.so>There is no mistaking that even now she\n"
"is overjoyed to be able to help you.\n"
"\n"
"<10.so>Promise me...that you will always\n"
"remember her. Promise me that.<11.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (20f)
msgctxt "talk05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I appreciate you saying that.<2.pa>\n"
"You are a good man."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (20f)
msgctxt "talk06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Thank you for saying so.<2.pa>\n"
"I truly appreciate it."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (20f)
#. 3: sound
#. 4: pause (20f)
msgctxt "talk07"
msgid ""
"<1.so>If you ever run into trouble,<2.pa> know that\n"
"you are always welcome here.\n"
"\n"
"<3.so>No matter the time, we shall all greet\n"
"you with open fins!\n"
"\n"
"Link...<4.pa> Thank you. Thank you from the\n"
"bottom of my heart."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (20f)
msgctxt "talk08"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Thank you, Link.<2.pa> You have saved us all.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I am certain that Mipha is thrilled to be\n"
"with you, as she ever was.\n"
"\n"
"I shall watch over Mipha's fight\n"
"from here, and yours as well."
msgstr ""

